item.title: CVE-2023-1095|2023-02-28T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- linux%20kernel%20netfilter%20subsystem.
item.description: In nf_tables_updtable, if nf_tables_table_enable returns an error, nft_trans_destroy is called to free the transaction object. nft_trans_destroy() calls list_del(), but the transaction was never placed on a list -- the list head is all zeroes, this results in a NULL pointer dereference.
